# Ticket Incident Hygiene 

#  Project Overview: ITIL Incident Management Hygiene 


##  Project Overview
The purpose of this project is to showcase a practical understanding of prioritizing tickets, managing queues and documenting by utilizng ITIL knowledge. 

Utilizing a simulator called Service Desk Simulator as the controlled environment and will use it to docuement reasoning, user commuinication, and troubleshooting approaches, and resolution documenting. 
While the simulator itself has its own model of its environment, the primary objective is to highlight triaging, remediating, and documentation.


