##  ITIL Priority Matrix

| Impact \ Urgency | High (Critical Block) | Medium (Work Impaired) | Low (Workaround Exists) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **High (Enterprise / Site-Wide)** | **P1 - Critical** | **P2 - High** | **P3 - Medium** |
| **Medium (Department / Team)** | **P2 - High** | **P3 - Medium** | **P4 - Low** |
| **Low (Single End-User)** | **P3 - Medium** | **P4 - Low** | **P4 - Low** |

